        <span class="ph-eyebrow">Perfume Care &amp; Storage</span>
        <h1 class="ph-title">Protect Every Bottle You <em>Love</em></h1>
        <p class="ph-sub">A fine fragrance is an investment worth caring for. In the UAE's heat and sunlight, how you store and handle your perfume decides whether it stays true for years — or fades in months. Here is how to keep every bottle performing at its best.</p>
        <div class="ph-meta">
          <span><span class="mi" aria-hidden="true">inventory_2</span>Storage done right</span>
